g.text: General:Interrupt = ( FIFO fills through SRI == CHx_INTR_CFG.DINQUANT ) AND ( empty FIFO entries >= CHx_INTR_CFG.DINLVL )Example:Interrupt = ( FIFO fills through SRI == 4 ) AND ( empty FIFO entries >= 4 )
